# Dubai Mall – Interactive DigiDeck

## Overview

This project is an interactive, DigiDeck-style presentation designed to showcase Dubai Mall as a global retail, lifestyle, and entertainment destination.

Instead of a traditional slide deck, this experience is built as a fully immersive, horizontally navigable web interface that combines storytelling, data visualization, and high-impact visuals.

---

## Key Features

* 🎬 Cinematic Hero Section (Video + fallback slideshow)
* ↔️ Horizontal Slide Navigation (DigiDeck-style experience)
* 📊 Data-driven storytelling (visitor metrics, retail stats, growth insights)
* 🛍 Interactive Retail & Entertainment modules
* 💎 Luxury-focused design language (gold + black theme)
* 📱 Responsive layout (optimized for desktop & adaptable for mobile)

---

## Sections Covered

1. Hero – Introduction & positioning
2. Why Dubai Mall – Scale, reach, and global impact
3. Retail – Leasing opportunities & formats
4. Luxury (Fashion Avenue) – Premium positioning
5. Dining & Lifestyle – Experience-driven engagement
6. Entertainment – Attractions & footfall drivers
7. Events & Partnerships – Global platform capabilities
8. Contact – Partner inquiry module

---

## Tech Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3 (custom layout, animations, responsive design)
* Vanilla JavaScript (navigation, interactions, dynamic rendering)

---

## How to Run Locally

1. Download or clone the repository
2. Ensure folder structure is intact:

```
project/
 ├── index.html
 ├── images/
 ├── video/
```

3. Open `index.html` in your browser

