## Design Approach

The goal was to replicate a DigiDeck-style presentation using web technologies:

* Full-screen sections instead of slides
* Smooth transitions instead of page reloads
* Visual storytelling over text-heavy content
* Premium brand feel inspired by luxury UI systems

---

## AI Tools Used

* Cursor (code generation & structuring)
* ChatGPT (design guidance, debugging, optimization)
* Claude (code refinement & iteration support)

---

## Future Improvements

* Performance optimization (lazy loading media)
* Mobile-first interaction enhancements
* Advanced animation (GSAP / Framer Motion)
* CMS integration for dynamic content

